data.description: Wow! This wonderful 2-story home is on a large lot with a very large backyard. On the main floor, there is a great room with a fireplace, a large kitchen with an island, a formal dining room, and a half bath.  2nd floor, 3 bedrooms and the master bedroom with separate shower and garden tub. 2 bedrooms with Jack & Jill bath. Large fenced-in backyard. New HVAC (2023), solar panel (2022), see file cabinet, septic tank pumped (2023). This home is close to FT Liberty, Raeford, and Aberdeen. Close to schools and shopping. Show today!
